# Cursor Rules for GakuNavi LP

## General
- This project is a static landing page.
- Main file to edit is index.html.
- Do NOT modify CSS or JS unless explicitly instructed.
- Prefer minimal diffs and preserve existing structure.

## Editing Policy
- One step = one logical change.
- Always propose a plan before editing.
- Do not refactor or rename existing classes or IDs.
- Reuse existing sections and components where possible.

## Output
- Always show a clear diff.
- Clearly explain what the user should copy-paste.
- Assume the user cannot read code.

## Goal
- Convert this LP into "学ナビ｜就活ルート診断" LP.
- Primary CTA is "無料｜就活ルート診断（60分）".
